benuRadiusMIB.name: benuRadiusMIB

revisions.description: Removed multiple instance indexes from BenuRadiusInstance.
Changed oid values for bRadiusProxyAuthTPSLowReached and bRadiusProxyAuthTPSHighReached.
Added units to processing times in bRadiusLatencyAuthTable
Updated notification assignments to comply with standards (RFC 2578).
Added radius proxy server Acct table

bRadiusAuthStatsInterval.name: bRadiusAuthStatsInterval
bRadiusAuthStatsInterval.description: The interval during which the measurements were accumulated. The interval index one indicates the latest interval for which statistics accumulation was completed. Older the statistics data, greater the interval index value. In a system supporting a history of n intervals with IntervalCount(1) and IntervalCount(n), the most and least recent intervals respectively, the following applies at the end of an interval: - discard the value of IntervalCount(n) - the value of IntervalCount(i) becomes that of IntervalCount(i+1) for 1 <= i < n - the value of IntervalCount(1) becomes that of CurrentCount.
